<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id6b045489-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e" identifier="/us/usc/t33/s6"><num value="6">§ 6.</num><heading> Free passage to harbor of Michigan City, Indiana</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The passage of vessels to and from the harbor of Michigan City, in Indiana, shall be free and not subject to toll or charge.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id6b04548a-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e">(R.S. § 5247.)</sourceCredit>
